    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A 1990s arcade take on the Cornhole game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hit the hole with your bag in the wooden board far from you to score a point. With each point you take life away from your opponent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TRAINING MODE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Train yourself by trying to score as many consecutive points as possible. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can choose to train as <i>Player 1</i> or as <i>Player 2</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you can achieve certain scores, you will get achievements. You will also get an additional life point at these scores, which will allow you to make an extra error.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you be able to reach, for example, 500 consecutive points?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only the best will succeed, and the score will be shown in the leaderboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299750/extras/a64785566d073fbbd86709e6f75f5280.avif?t=1731704563\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3299750/extras_big/a64785566d073fbbd86709e6f75f5280.avif?t=1731704563 width=800 height=398 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;VERSUS CPU&quot; MODE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Throw yourself into fascinating challenges against the computer, with three different modes to choose from:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >EASY</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MEDIUM</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HARD</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you win every duel?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&quot;VERSUS MODE&quot; - PLAYER VS PLAYER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If, on the other hand, you are a believer in the old days, invite a friend over and play your duel using the same keyboard!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
